{"tid":174660,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有啲post推唔起？","createTime":"2017-03-27T03:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T10:13:13.000Z","uid":35370,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6a9c778801771b5e0b7b27ecbdaedf9a10347f","tid":174660,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:30:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/174593/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/174593/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n無論講故台定吹水台都推唔起個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係唔會浮返上面"},{"pid":"858ae2563ebe1905d9b9dc174d05002b12dbc99d","tid":174660,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:32:08.000Z","msg":"點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66688e9dfa661c224e5aacd6905171ce2b719309","tid":174660,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"曲線叫人推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ebfc7d60bad9b3a5cd7b6809042fc28cb93ddf","tid":174660,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T04:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曲線叫人推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀<br />\n初初得我一個人留言個陣係推唔起嘅<br />\n但後來第二頁，有另一個巴打留言之後<br />\n個post先至識得浮返上水面<br />\n我都唔知點解會咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603f02d5d18f9d07a6c49ca684bd482aab8eb610","tid":174660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2408742a826a01bce13d089ff8eeb4dd24fbf19c","tid":174660,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曲線叫人推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀<br />\n初初得我一個人留言個陣係推唔起嘅<br />\n但後來第二頁，有另一個巴打留言之後<br />\n個post先至識得浮返上水面<br />\n我都唔知點解會咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常一個人推post係推唔到，所以我之前先質疑點解蔣生可以自己推post<br />\n詳情可以睇番我之前個熱門系統post"},{"pid":"c8cc8c30a9a649c59325d4f83a50168e84f187d9","tid":174660,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"我有個post之前都係咁<br />\n正常有人留言，果個台會彈個post出黎<br />\n唔知點解之前唔浮面，後黎又正常返"},{"pid":"7671f88862b434903e48304748be50c31b4c50f4","tid":174660,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:15:42.000Z","msg":"我一日最多推 post 兩次，<br />\n有時候係更新文章或語句，<br />\n但都竟然推唔起自己個 post，<br />\n反而有人可以頻繁推 post。<br />\n<br />\n我都好想 admin 可以解答下。"},{"pid":"341d1836595095f6d62fd2a4af12dbfa45488581","tid":174660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:35:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一日最多推 post 兩次，<br />\n有時候係更新文章或語句，<br />\n但都竟然推唔起自己個 post，<br />\n反而有人可以頻繁推 post。<br />\n<br />\n我都好想 admin 可以解答下。</blockquote><br />\n沉左一個月無人掂過既post就話唔推得啫<br />\n屌佢老味keep住有推有理既post過左一個月都推唔到,咩道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知高登舊時真係咩post都係推得1個月就推唔起<br />\n但舊規矩係差,黎到新地方就改改佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28f5422e03e4264211cc84418fdc3eb0e7f81fb","tid":174660,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我一日最多推 post 兩次，<br />\n有時候係更新文章或語句，<br />\n但都竟然推唔起自己個 post，<br />\n反而有人可以頻繁推 post。<br />\n<br />\n我都好想 admin 可以解答下。</blockquote><br />\n沉左一個月無人掂過既post就話唔推得啫<br />\n屌佢老味keep住有推有理既post過左一個月都推唔到,咩道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知高登舊時真係咩post都係推得1個月就推唔起<br />\n但舊規矩係差,黎到新地方就改改佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個 post 係月頭開，<br />\n大概係20日左右，我推唔到都無所謂。<br />\n見到時事台有人可以不斷自推，<br />\n我就真係充滿疑問，連登真係縱容打手？<br />\n<br />\n站務台，可唔可以有個合理回應？"},{"pid":"e7e4a3a5bdca48465b56f87776fedca1a47dc2fd","tid":174660,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"上熱門個標準又唔知點計出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19c3fb37c1091688884040a7db46a242961d45b","tid":174660,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上熱門個標準又唔知點計出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾百正評都唔撚夠啲無聊po熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c180325f9f0b780a162fe6d1b49d1b22074ec540","tid":174660,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上熱門個標準又唔知點計出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾百正評都唔撚夠啲無聊po熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不嬲都黑商作業架啦"},{"pid":"c4f1e8469c367478ecec3f5516d02687510db16e","tid":174660,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上熱門個標準又唔知點計出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n[認真]麻煩ADMIN解釋一下連登熱門既算法或者準則<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/167459/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/167459/page/1?ref=web</a>"},{"pid":"060373ab90aff4dbbead8fb47c03146e1e29147e","tid":174660,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T22:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上熱門個標準又唔知點計出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n[認真]麻煩ADMIN解釋一下連登熱門既算法或者準則<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/167459/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/167459/page/1?ref=web</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6de8aa26afba77c2b461b69e3d33b037509c96","tid":174660,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等答案"},{"pid":"92e0f7464c3215a4c3faa9aa3ee982e495e23048","tid":174660,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等答案</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c1c946ca404e95d35464f10345016f3d47283c","tid":174660,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:34:36.000Z","msg":"雖然提防中介係好事，<br />\n但點解蔣巴可以自推到，<br />\n而我地一般會員唔得？<br />\n公平公正公開係好重要。　<br />\n<br />\n麻煩解答我地疑惑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/152823/page/10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/152823/page/10</a>"},{"pid":"507ebf08bfe5f925f8299b0440fb7f1847d5f7cb","tid":174660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:50:14.000Z","msg":"新post舊post總之全部自推就唔撚得<br />\n係咪痴線?今日娛樂開既聯賽post,新post黎,我自推都係想有人睇到<br />\n平時都唔留意,因為通常都係不停推,唔會撳返出去<br />\n咁今晚手痕望下,屌你老母推完係就係寫住[不久前]<br />\n但唔係推到上頁頭,而係數落左十幾個post,喺另一個[14分鐘前]既post下面<br />\n要跟住有其他巴打推post先上得返頁頭<br />\n即係話呢幾個月我自推其實都幾撚多餘,因為吹水台基本上唔會顯示到<br />\n結果有啲潛在其實會想投既巴打,一路都唔知有呢個比賽<br />\n連尼住呢個垃圾機制打壓連登自發活動根本可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365265da69e2530c896f705238eac2572d3443bb","tid":174660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"仲要累到我地比人招口實屌我地低投票率<br />\n其實最根本係因為自推方面有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到有人有票唔知有得投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a435e153b155d26231289bd0baa23724b67c0a0e","tid":174660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新post舊post總之全部自推就唔撚得<br />\n係咪痴線?今日娛樂開既聯賽post,新post黎,我自推都係想有人睇到<br />\n平時都唔留意,因為通常都係不停推,唔會撳返出去<br />\n咁今晚手痕望下,屌你老母推完係就係寫住[不久前]<br />\n但唔係推到上頁頭,而係數落左十幾個post,喺另一個[14分鐘前]既post下面<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲要呢個只係娛樂台入面分台既情況,咁試想像喺吹水台個post會去左邊?</span><br />\n要跟住有其他巴打推post先上得返頁頭<br />\n即係話呢幾個月我自推其實都幾撚多餘,因為吹水台基本上唔會顯示到<br />\n結果有啲潛在其實會想投既巴打,一路都唔知有呢個比賽<br />\n連尼住呢個垃圾機制打壓連登自發活動根本可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"22fc00ce25352db25f8c364bc1f328756d243ff3","tid":174660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個forum唔係方便巴打交流,會唔會好本末倒置呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7543527da336e9668d0a939dd6a471ab462c7c7","tid":174660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"叫你開發置頂功能你唔理都算<br />\n原來最基本推post都搞到啲巴打推到一仆一碌<br />\n真係好離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ba1f6e6a535c0ff6f6ce0144cd2f93443b4db8","tid":174660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e13797b76e3b5f17e7f1e852d01945fef48c7c1","tid":174660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}